entries.s_109: Scanning... [The Compactor 3000 jiggles.]  ... Greetings, adventurer! Keep our cave clean by depositing your trash here.
entries.s_113: Proccessing... [The Compactor 3000's lights start to blink.] We realize you may find things during your adventure that you have no use for. Help keep our caves clean by depositing unwanted items here. We give credit rewards to those to help us keep our caves clean.
entries.s_115: Hmm.. I have some trash for you.
entries.s_117: Processing... We give top credits for unwanted items. The Compactor 3000 thanks you.
entries.s_119: I don't have any trash at the moment.
entries.s_121: [The Compactor 3000 shuts down, waiting for the next customer.]
